trans-unit.source: Represents a workflow queue.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en arbeidsflytkø.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Workflow queues are used to pass messages between a host or host services and activities in a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Arbeidsflyten køer brukes til å sende meldinger mellom vert eller vertstjenestene og aktiviteter i en arbeidsflyt.

trans-unit.source: Any activity can create a WorkflowQueue by calling <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, and a host, a service, or another activity can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A> to add an item to that WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: Alle aktiviteter kan opprette en WorkflowQueue ved å kalle <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, og vert, en tjeneste eller en annen aktivitet kan ringe <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A>å legge til et element i den WorkflowQueue.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can subscribe to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable> event to be notified when an item arrives on the WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: Du kan abonnere på de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable>hendelsen som skal varsles når et element kommer til WorkflowQueue.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable>

trans-unit.source: You can use <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A> to examine an item at the beginning of the WorkflowQueue and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A> to remove an item from the WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A>å undersøke et element i begynnelsen av WorkflowQueue og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A>til å fjerne et element fra WorkflowQueue.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each WorkflowQueue is associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService> that you can use to perform other management operations on the WorkflowQueue, such as deleting the queue.
trans-unit.target: Hver WorkflowQueue er knyttet til en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>som du kan bruke til å utføre andre administrasjonsoperasjoner på WorkflowQueue, for eksempel sletting av køen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A> exposes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService> associated with this WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A>Viser den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>som er forbundet med denne WorkflowQueue.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A>

trans-unit.source: Removes and returns the object at the beginning of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: You can check <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Count%2A> to determine whether the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> is empty before you call Dequeue, or you can catch the <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan kontrollere <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Count%2A>å finne ut om den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>er tom før du kaller Dequeue, eller du kan få tak i <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Count%2A>

trans-unit.target: Legger til et objekt på slutten av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the object at the beginning of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref> without removing it.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer objektet i begynnelsen av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref> uten å fjerne den.

trans-unit.source: This method is similar to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A> method, but Peek does not modify the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er lik <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A>metoden, men kikking endrer ikke <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can check <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Count%2A> to determine whether the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> is empty before you call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A>, or you can catch the <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an item is delivered on this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når et element leveres i denne <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This event is only used for processing that must occur synchronously with event delivery to the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen brukes bare for behandling som må gjøres synkront med hendelsen levering arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The event handler may execute on a non-workflow thread so access to any shared workflow object, for example, any <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>, must be protected.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsesbehandlingen kan kjøre på en ikke-arbeidsflyten tråd slik tilgang til noen delt arbeidsflyt-objekt, for eksempel noen <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>, må den være beskyttet.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an item is available on this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når et element er tilgjengelig på dette <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The QueueItemAvailable event is raised in an asynchronous manner.
trans-unit.target: QueueItemAvailable denne hendelsen oppstår i en asynkron måte.

trans-unit.source: The sender for the QueueItemAvailable event will be the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> of the subscribing <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.
trans-unit.target: Avsenderen for hendelsen QueueItemAvailable blir den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>for abonnementer <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>
